@startuml
!theme plain
title Firmware Startup Sequence

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam ArrowColor #333333
skinparam FontName Arial
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #555555

participant "Zephyr\nKernel" as zephyr #D3D3D3
participant "hvb_controller\n(App)" as app #AED6F1
participant "Virtual Channel\nProviders" as vcp #FAD7A0
participant "Domain Runtime\nLibrary" as domain #A9DFBF
participant "Frontend\nAdapters" as front #AED6F1

== Phase 1: Hardware Safe State ==

zephyr -> zephyr : Initialize devices\n(init priorities)
app -> vcp : Configure output-enable\nto safe disabled state
app -> vcp : Write safe Output Drive Level\n(DAC code zero) to all outputs

== Phase 2: Configuration ==

app -> app : Discover virtual channels\n(devicetree + Kconfig)
app -> app : Load persistent settings\n(NVS / Settings)

== Phase 3: Domain Initialization ==

app -> domain : Initialize with channel\ncapabilities and config
domain -> domain : Set up protection policy,\nrecovery state, calibration
domain -> domain : Evaluate operating mode\n(Normal or Automatic)

== Phase 4: Runtime Start ==

app -> vcp : Start channel runtime\nprocessing
app -> front : Start Modbus adapter
app -> front : Start shell adapter

== Phase 5: Operating Mode ==

alt Normal Mode
  front -> domain : Wait for remote\nfrontend commands
else Automatic Mode
  domain -> domain : Validate auto-start config\nper channel
  domain -> vcp : Request channel enable\nvia domain command path
  vcp --> domain : Measurement Snapshots
  domain -> domain : Apply ramp policy,\nprotection remains\nfinal authority
end

@enduml
